To clarify, this is not El Dorado. El Dorado (the golden one) refers to a tribal chief who is said to cover himself in gold dust and dive into a lake.

This, however, is the following:

Seven Cities of Gold
Cibola and Quivira
City of the Caesars
The golden city that was mislabelled as 
And every single  in Latin America


As to what is happening, SCP-2955 routinely  gold nuggets which adds a surplus to Latin American gold. The Conquistadors decided to just grab everything that is made of gold, and SCP-2955 made a desperate attempt to escape them, hence its anomalous effect is simply a very drastic defence mechanism.

The last portion of the article was SCP-2955 deciding that the Foundation ultimately are  (i.e. the Conquistadors).








